name: Glitchtoshi v.3
description: Glitchtoshi was a series I first started on Rarible and decided to bring over to HEN. This series was created as a homage to the anonymous alias ‘Satoshi Nakamoto’ used by the person/people who created Bitcoin. The person in the image is named Satoshi Nakamoto, but does not admit to being the creator of Bitcoin. This piece was made by using Procreate, Photoshop, & After Effects. The size of the file uploaded is 22mb, but if you are the owner of this piece, DM me and I can send you the full size file (43mb). Twitter: @crypto_wook
